 language or location) and provide enhanced, personalized features.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 <strong>Targeting or Advertising Cookies:<\/strong> These cookies are used to deliver advertisements more relevant to you and your interests. They also help limit the number of times you see an ad and measure the effectiveness of our marketing campaigns.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_How_We_Use_Cookies\"><\/span>3. How We Use Cookies<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UM.Marketing uses cookies for various purposes:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 To remember your preferences and settings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 To improve the performance and usability of the website.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 To analyze traffic and user behavior on our site.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 To provide you with personalized content and advertising.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Third-Party_Cookies\"><\/span>4. Third-Party Cookies<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We may also use third-party cookies, which are set by a different domain than UM.Marketing. These third-party cookies help us with marketing, analytics, and other services to enhance your experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_How_to_Manage_Cookies\"><\/span>5. How to Manage Cookies<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings at any time. However, please note that disabling certain cookies may affect your browsing experience and some features of the site may not function properly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To manage cookies, refer to your browser\u2019s help section for detailed instructions:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 <a href=\"https:\/\/support.google.com\/chrome\/answer\/95647\">Google Chrome<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 <a href=\"https:\/\/support.mozilla.org\/en-US\/kb\/enable-and-disable-cookies-website-preferences\">Mozilla Firefox<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 <a href=\"https:\/\/support.apple.com\/guide\/safari\/manage-cookies-and-website-data-sfri11471\/mac\">Safari<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u2022 <a href=\"https:\/\/support.microsoft.com\/en-us\/help\/4468242\/microsoft-edge-browsing-data-and-privacy\">Microsoft Edge<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Consent\"><\/span>6. Consent<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>By using our website, you consent to the use of cookies as outlined in this policy. You can withdraw your consent at any time by adjusting your browser settings or contacting us for further assistance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7_Changes_to_the_Cookie_Policy\"><\/span>7. Changes to the Cookie Policy<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, so we encourage you to review it regularly to stay informed about how we use cookies.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"8_Contact_Us\"><\/span>8. Contact Us<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any questions about our Cookie Policy, please contact us at:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>UM.Marketing<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Email: <a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24.2424px; text-decoration-line: none; display: inline-block; margin: 0px; color: rgb(29, 29, 27); font-weight: 700; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(29, 29, 27); font-family: Manrope; font-size: 18.648px; white-space-collapse: collapse;\" href=\"mailto:team@unknown.marketing\">team@unknown.marketing<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This text provides a clear overview of how cookies are used on your site and complies with common regulations like GDPR. Feel free to adjust it to your specific needs!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>At UM.Ma